extendedInfo.description: If you are Mindless Behavior's fan, this app is right for you. Whenever you want to check Mindless Behavior's lyrics, just open this app and choose the lyrics that you want. You don't have to access the internet to get the lyrics. We provide all Mindless Behavior's lyrics here. In the Album tab, you can choose lyrics based on the album. In All lyrics tab, all of Mindless Behavior's lyrics are here. You can quickly search the lyrics by using the search bar at the top of the page.Hope you guy enjoy using this app as much as I enjoy developing it. :)--------------------------------Main Features --------------------------------- Lyrics categorized by album - Show all lyrics - Search lyrics--------------------------------List of albums --------------------------------- #1 Girl- All Around the World--------------------------------List of lyrics --------------------------------- #1 Girl- All Around The World- Future- Girls Talking Bout- Gone- Hello- Hook It Up- Intro- Keep Her On The Low- Missing You- Mrs. Right- My Girl- Uh-Oh- Used To Be- I Lean (Lose It)- Pretty Girl- I'm Falling- Ready For Love- Band-Aid- Forever- Video- Brightside- Lookin For Ya- Bang Bang Bang- Your Favorite Song- House Party
